Create a tsibble object

Create a tsibble object

tsibble(..., key = key_vars(), index)

# S3 method for tbl_ts
print(x, ...)

key_vars(...)

Arguments

...

A set of name-value pairs.
key

Unquoted variable(s) indicating the key variables for tsibble, used in combination with key_vars().
index

An unquoted variable indicating the time index variable
x

A tsibble object.
...

Extra arguments.
...

Unquoted variable(s).

Value

A tsibble object.

See also

tibble::tibble

Examples

   ts_df <- tsibble(
     Date = rep(seq(as.Date("2017-01-01"), by = 1, length = 10), 2),
     Group = rep(c("A", "B"), each = 10),
     Value = rnorm(20),
     key = key_vars(Group), index = Date
   )
   print(ts_df)
